{"tid":566437,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咪又係⋯ 【強國男迷港女】有港女唱完賣肉　老闆拔槍逼陪酒","createTime":"2018-02-20T02:59:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T04:19:10.000Z","uid":121464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6586dd934a57fc297fe0c4e3efb81e835a289b0a","tid":566437,"uid":121464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T02:59:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20180220/2_572381_0/-強國男迷港女-有港女唱完賣肉-老闆拔槍逼陪酒\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20180220%2F2_572381_0%2F-%E5%BC%B7%E5%9C%8B%E7%94%B7%E8%BF%B7%E6%B8%AF%E5%A5%B3-%E6%9C%89%E6%B8%AF%E5%A5%B3%E5%94%B1%E5%AE%8C%E8%B3%A3%E8%82%89-%E8%80%81%E9%97%86%E6%8B%94%E6%A7%8D%E9%80%BC%E9%99%AA%E9%85%92&d=K1RdEzaG75tE%2F7zQtc754XadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=b0e87955\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20180220%2F2_572381_0%2F-%E5%BC%B7%E5%9C%8B%E7%94%B7%E8%BF%B7%E6%B8%AF%E5%A5%B3-%E6%9C%89%E6%B8%AF%E5%A5%B3%E5%94%B1%E5%AE%8C%E8%B3%A3%E8%82%89-%E8%80%81%E9%97%86%E6%8B%94%E6%A7%8D%E9%80%BC%E9%99%AA%E9%85%92&h=0cd18ee1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20180220/2_572381_0/-強國男迷港女-有港女唱完賣肉-老闆拔槍逼陪酒</a><br />\n<br />\nsource: Apple daily<br />\n<br />\n「我知道有些女孩子北上登台時，她們不是想唱歌，我自己真心喜歡唱歌，所以就賺錢唱歌。但她們會陪客人睡覺，賺多一筆錢。這筆錢隨時比歌酬多很多。」港人蘇慧恩（Ophelia）經常北上夜場登台，坦言有香港女孩子唱歌之外，還會出賣肉體。最恐怖的，曾被夜店老闆拔槍威嚇逼陪酒。 <br />\n<br />\n內地夜場，總是品流複雜，「其實坦白說，在內地會有人問價，會有人向你問價，但自己決定做不做。我知道有些女孩子北上登台時，她們不是想唱歌，我自己真心喜歡唱歌，所以就賺錢唱歌。但她們會陪客人睡覺，賺多一筆錢。這筆錢隨時比歌酬多很多。」 <br />\n<br />\nOphelia說，自己亦試過被人問價，「其實都有很多人問過我，有很多，但我不會的。當然拒絕啦，我表明不做這些，只會唱歌。不要說內地，就算在香港，都會有老闆向你問價，你自己可以決定是否做。」 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登仔logic: 咪又係⋯"},{"pid":"5d6e7d53529df6d6177733250b202ae719797baa","tid":566437,"uid":53554,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T03:06:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"33a7670e5245f68bf68717a984b80c9c394435ef","tid":566437,"uid":18607,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T03:08:00.000Z","msg":"每個人都有個價！"},{"pid":"58afe3bdf247a7574e55eb58c03cf2433c9b8901","tid":566437,"uid":22554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T03:09:27.000Z","msg":"其實又唔係明星，　有乜必要搵香港人去唱，<br />\n<br />\n唔需要有名氣，　求其搵個大陸女仔都得啦"},{"pid":"5767c091385baa320198259d2dd3d725f1c35baf","tid":566437,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T04:19:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/20/121858_989cf09893753da41bee2cdac09f5fb8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F20%2F121858_989cf09893753da41bee2cdac09f5fb8.jpg&h=e6d56e13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n🇭🇺華杜斯(傑志)<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">2018-02-20<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">(今晚)</span></strong>20:00 亞冠盃 傑志 vs 全北汽車(韓國)\t@香港大球場</span>"}]}